<body>
<div class="header">
    <header>
        <div class="nav-title">
            <p id="nav-title-name">Badminton Club</p>
        </div>
    </header>
</div>
<div class="background">
    <div class="image">
        <img id="pc-img" src="https://wallpaperaccess.com/full/1429498.jpg">
        <img id="mobile-img" src="/images/mobile-layout/badminton-mobile.jpg">
    </div>
    <div class="headline">
        <p id="typography-head">환영합니다!</p>
        <p id="typography-description">가입 신청을 하시면 세명컴퓨터고등학교 2022년도 배드민턴 동아리 면접 기회가 주어집니다.</p>
    </div>
    <hr id="between-headline-container">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="title">2022 배드민턴부 신청서</div>
        <div class="notice">
            <p id="typography-caption"><span class="star">*</span> 표시 항목은 필수 입력 사항입니다.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
            <label>학번<span class="star">*</span></label>
            <input type="tel" id="studentId" pattern=”[0-9]*” maxlength="5" placeholder="Ex) 30710" required>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
            <label>이름<span class="star">*</span></label>
            <input type="text" id="name" placeholder="Ex) 홍길동" required>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
            <label>전화번호 </label>
            <p id="mini_notice">(합격여부 공지용)</p>
            <input type="tel" id="tel" pattern="[0-1]{3}[0-9]{4}[0-9]{4}" maxlength="11" placeholder="Ex) 01012345678" required>
        </div>
        <hr id="between-input-button">
        <div>
            <button class="btn" onclick="signup()">신청하기!</button>
        </div>
        <div class="popup">
            <div class="popup-page">
                <p id="popup-title">감사합니다!</p>
                <p id="popup-description">면접신청이 성공적으로 완료되었습니다. 면접에 꼭 참여해주시길 바랍니다.</p>
                <p id="interview"><a id="link" href="">면접장소 및 일시 확인하기 ></a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="copyright">
        <p>© 2022 SMC Badminton. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</div>
<script defer src="/js/index.js"></script>
<script defer src="/js/confetti.js"></script>
</body>
